## SavedObjectUnsanitizedDoc type

Describes Saved Object documents from OpenSearchDashboards &lt; 7.0.0 which don't have a `references` root property defined. This type should only be used in migrations.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type SavedObjectUnsanitizedDoc<T = unknown> = SavedObjectDoc<T> & Partial<Referencable>;
```
